        <Parent_String>religious schools (institutions) [300343470], schools (institutions) [300266108], educational institutions [300386368], institutions by activity [300312238], institutions (organizations) [300026004], organizations (groups) [300025948], Organizations (hierarchy name) [300234770], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
